Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"
Set WindowBar Rings

Hide
Type "rm -f hello.py"
Enter
Type "npm run dev --silent"
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "Write a python script that prints 'Hello from OpenCLI!' to hello.py"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 15s

Type "/exit"
Enter
Sleep 1s
